<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Binary Bean</title>

<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600;700&family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400;500&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
/* ================= ROOT ================= */
:root {
  --cream: #f5f2ed;
  --warm-white: #f0c27e;
  --gold: #e0952a;
  --dark: #1c1510;
  --text: #3a3028;
  --text-muted: #7a6d62;
  --border: #e2dbd3;
  --card-bg: #f9f6f2;
  --gold-btn: #6b5022;
  --white: #ffffff;
  --overlay: rgba(30, 22, 10, 0.55);
}

/* ================= GLOBAL RESET ================= */
* {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  background: var(--cream);
  overflow-x: hidden;
  color: var(--text);
}

/* ================= LOGIN ================= */
.login-section {
  height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
}

.login-box {
  width: 360px;
  background: white;
  padding: 40px;
  border-radius: 16px;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.input-group {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.input-group input {
  padding: 10px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  border: 1px solid #ccc;
}

.login-btn {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 12px;
  border: none;
  background: var(--gold-btn);
  color: white;
  border-radius: 999px;
}

/* ================= MAIN WRAPPER ================= */
#main-site {
  display: none;
}

/* ================= NAV ================= */
nav {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 18px 60px;
  background: transparent;
  position: absolute;
  width: 100%;
  top: 0;
  z-index: 100;
  color: white;
}

.logo {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 1.6rem;
  font-weight: 600;
}

.nav-links a {
  color: white;
  text-decoration: none;
  margin: 0 15px;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
}

.order-btn {
  background: var(--gold-btn);
  color: white;
  padding: 8px 20px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
}

/* ================= HERO ================= */
.hero {
  position: relative;
  height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: flex-start;
  padding-left: 100px;
  color: white;
  overflow: hidden;
}

#bg-image {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509042239860-f550ce710b93?w=1600') center/cover no-repeat;
  filter: brightness(0.6);
}

.overlay {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: var(--overlay);
}

.hero-content {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  max-width: 500px;
  text-align: left;
}

.tagline {
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  opacity: 0.9;
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 5px 15px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  border-radius: 999px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.hero h1 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
  line-height: 1.2;
}

.hero h1 span {
  color: var(--gold);
  font-style: italic;
}

.subtitle {
  margin-top: 20px;
  opacity: 0.85;
  max-width: 400px;
  line-height: 1.8;
}

.hero-buttons {
  margin-top: 30px;
  display: flex;
  gap: 15px;
}

.btn-primary {
  background: var(--gold);
  color: white;
  padding: 12px 30px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 500;
  border: none;
}

.btn-outline {
  background: transparent;
  color: white;
  padding: 12px 30px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 500;
  border: 1px solid white;
}

/* ================= MENU SECTION ================= */
.menu-section {
  padding: 80px 60px;
  text-align: center;
}

.section-title {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 50px;
  color: var(--dark);
}

.menu-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  gap: 30px;
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: auto;
}

.menu-card {
  background: transparent;
  border: none;
}

.card-img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 250px;
  overflow: hidden;
  border-radius: 12px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.card-img img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  display: block;
}

.card-body h2 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  color: var(--dark);
}

.menu-list {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.menu-list li {
  padding: 8px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  color: var(--text-muted);
}

.view-link {
  color: var(--gold);
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 500;
}

/* ================= ABOUT SECTION ================= */
.about-section {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 50px;
  padding: 80px;
  align-items: center;
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: auto;
}

.img-wrapper {
  position: relative;
  border-radius: 18px;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.img-wrapper img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  display: block;
}

.est-badge {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -20px;
  right: -20px;
  background: var(--gold);
  color: white;
  width: 100px;
  height: 100px;
  border-radius: 16px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-weight: bold;
  text-align: center;
  line-height: 1.2;
}

.about-content .small-title {
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  padding: 5px 15px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  display: inline-block;
  border-radius: 999px;
}

.about-content h2 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  color: var(--dark);
}

.about-content p {
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}

/* ================= RESPONSIVE ================= */
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  nav { padding: 15px 20px; }
  .hero { padding-left: 30px; }
  .about-section { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 40px; }
  .menu-section { padding: 60px 30px; }
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- ================= LOGIN ================= -->
<section class="login-section" id="login-page">
  <div class="login-box">
    <h2>Login to Binary Bean</h2>

    <form onsubmit="handleLogin(event)">
      <div class="input-group">
        <label>Email</label>
        <input type="email" id="email" required>
      </div>

      <div class="input-group">
        <label>Password</label>
        <input type="password" id="password" required>
      </div>

      <button class="login-btn">Login</button>
    </form>

    <p id="login-message"></p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ================= MAIN SITE ================= -->
<div id="main-site">

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="logo">Binary Bean</div>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#">Home</a>
    <a href="#">Menu</a>
    <a href="#">About</a>
    <a href="#">Contact</a>
  </div>
  <a href="#" class="order-btn">Order Online</a>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div id="bg-image"></div>
  <div class="overlay"></div>

  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="tagline">Artisanal Coffee & Premium Tea</div>
    <h1>Where Every Cup <span>Tells a Story</span></h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Experience the unique fusion of slow-brewed tea and hand-roasted coffee in a space designed for connection and calm.</p>
    <div class="hero-buttons">
      <a href="#" class="btn-primary">Explore Menu</a>
      <a href="#" class="btn-outline">Visit Us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- MENU -->
<section class="menu-section">
  <h2 class="section-title">Our Offerings</h2>
  
  <div class="menu-grid">

    <div class="menu-card">
      <div class="card-img">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509042239860-f550ce710b93?w=800">
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2>Signature Coffee</h2>
        <ul class="menu-list">
          <li>Espresso</li>
          <li>Americano</li>
          <li>Cappuccino</li>
          <li>Latte</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#" class="view-link">View Category →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="menu-card">
      <div class="card-img">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556679343-c7306c1976bc?w=800">
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2>Premium Tea</h2>
        <ul class="menu-list">
          <li>Green Tea</li>
          <li>Black Tea</li>
          <li>Herbal Infusions</li>
          <li>Iced Tea</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#" class="view-link">View Category →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="menu-card">
      <div class="card-img">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1530610476181-d83430b64dcd?w=800">
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2>Fresh Pastries</h2>
        <ul class="menu-list">
          <li>Croissant</li>
          <li>Muffins</li>
          <li>Cakes & Slices</li>
          <li>Cookies</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#" class="view-link">View Category →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section class="about-section">

  <div class="img-wrapper">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1495474472287-4d71bcdd2085">
    <div class="est-badge">Est.<br>2026</div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-content">
    <div class="small-title">Our Philosophy</div>
    <h2>Crafting a Third Space</h2>
    <p>CoffTea began with a simple observation: the world is divided into coffee people and tea people, but the ritual of a warm drink is universal.</p>
    <p>We created a sanctuary where artisanal espresso meets ceremonial tea. A place where you can find the high-energy focus of a dark roast or the meditative calm of a steep.</p>
  </div>

</section>

</div>

<!-- ================= LOGIN SCRIPT ================= -->
<script>
function handleLogin(event) {
  event.preventDefault();

  const email = document.getElementById("email").value;
  const password = document.getElementById("password").value;

  if (email === "admin@binarybean.com" && password === "123456") {
    document.getElementById("login-page").style.display = "none";
    document.getElementById("main-site").style.display = "block";
  } else {
    document.getElementById("login-message").innerText = "Invalid login";
  }
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
